{"tid":2206800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新任英國駐華大使吳若蘭欣然接受駐英大使劉曉明所贈送的「習語錄」 聲稱要建立進取的英中合作","createTime":"2020-09-17T17:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T22:53:05.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"65d46cda43e9b0abd3958e476a5e7dfcd0f1cf8e","tid":2206800,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:14:19.000Z","msg":"新任英國駐華大使吳若蘭（Caroline Wilson）啟程飛往北京前，會見中國駐英大使劉曉明，並獲贈「習語錄」，聲稱要建立「進取的英中合作」（Ambitious UK-China collaboration）。在刻下英中關係勢成水火，其親華論調實在讓人難以想像－－而接受猶如「毛語錄」般高舉個人崇拜的「禮物」，更是協助中共大外宣，難看至極。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1306530995571765248?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1306530995571765248%3F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=8cfc405f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1306530995571765248%3F&h=2974b010\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1306530995571765248?</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/photos/a.645858435565493/2336535789831074/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNathanLawKC%2Fphotos%2Fa.645858435565493%2F2336535789831074%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=138dc592\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/photos/a.645858435565493/2336535789831074/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"4e38818db777fec59f11e61490b2810fa88eb3d2","tid":2206800,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:14:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1306530995571765248?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1306530995571765248%3Fs%3D20&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOGrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=473103ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?